   Genotyping charges are based on the source of support for the research
   project.
     __________________________________________________________________


                               Current Pricing
     __________________________________________________________________


   Research projects supported by grants or intramural research funds
   from one of the twelve supporting institutes No Charge
   Research projects supported by grants or intramural research funds
   from an NIH Institute not supporting CIDR,
   or from another government or non-profit institution $1.50 per genotype
   Research projects supported by for-profit enterprises $3.50 per
   genotype

   Collaboration with statistical genetics consultants incurs no
   additional charge for approved projects.

